## Go to ImageStreams
Create ImageStreams -> copy imagestream.yaml (make sure   namespace: nav220161-dev is replaced with your namespace) --> create imagestream


## Go to BuidConfig

Open BuildConfigs -> Create BuildConfig -> Copy build-config.yaml (Make sure you change the namespace with your namespace) -> Create

## Check Build
A build has triggered, check the status

## Build Completes
When build complete, check Imagestream, scoll down and check image is created

## Create Deployement binded with ImageStream

Workload >> Deployment >> Copy deployment.yaml (change namespace) > Create >> Check Pod status

### Go to BuildConfig 
Trigger a new build 

## Build Completed
When build completes, it will update the image

## Check Deployment
Pod must be restarted with new image